Zarina Hassan is throwing shade back at fans who’ve been hating on her everyday selfie life.  Many have been ranting and whining about how she ‘joy rides’ at work, saying that the only thing she does all day long is taking photos. Well, the boss lady has come out to respond to her naysayers. The mega star said her sons will be hiring them haters soon. She wrote, “Ati she wakes up everyday to take pics but has no job, try it slay cartoons.My sons will be hiring you soon. New Bosses In The Making.”